tanren/specs/rust-testing-hard-cutover-phase0/phase-events.jsonl:374:{"schema_version":"1.0.0","event_id":"019dba86-7c9f-7aa1-acd1-8a7c7952a547","spec_id":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000c01","phase":"investigate","agent_session_id":"cli-session","timestamp":"2026-04-23T13:27:49.151743Z","origin_kind":"tool_primary","tool":"revise_task","payload":{"event_type":"task_revised","task_id":"019db58b-b492-7423-925a-80190e82b708","spec_id":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000c01","revised_description":"Produce the Phase 0 orchestration meta-readiness report and explicitly capture the terminal gate state from actual execution evidence. When final just ci is red, the report must still be delivered with blocker evidence and an explicit remediation handoff task reference.","revised_acceptance":[{"id":"t13-ac1","description":"Meta report captures strengths, frictions, and proposed mitigations.","measurable":"Report includes an explicit GO/NO-GO readiness recommendation with rationale."},{"id":"t13-ac2","description":"Report records terminal gate status using concrete evidence.","measurable":"Report includes latest just check and just ci results, references supporting gate artifacts/logs, and states whether terminal closure rule is currently satisfied."},{"id":"t13-ac3","description":"Terminal-gate failure path includes explicit remediation handoff.","measurable":"If just ci is failing, report references a dedicated remediation task and names the failing gate and affected file scope."}],"reason":"Root cause includes acceptance-criteria ambiguity: T13 is a reporting task, but previous acceptance wording conflated report delivery with terminal gate remediation. This revision keeps T13 focused on evidence-backed readiness reporting while requiring explicit remediation linkage when just ci is red."}}
tanren/specs/rust-testing-hard-cutover-phase0/phase-events.jsonl:375:{"schema_version":"1.0.0","event_id":"019dba86-b4d9-7bb1-a73b-c5fea3e27664","spec_id":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000c01","phase":"investigate","agent_session_id":"cli-session","timestamp":"2026-04-23T13:28:03.545836Z","origin_kind":"tool_primary","tool":"create_task","payload":{"event_type":"task_created","task":{"id":"019dba86-b4d9-7bb1-a73b-c5e780404a72","spec_id":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000c01","title":"T14 Strict Mutation Gate Remediation For Phase 0 Final CI","description":"Resolve the strict mutation-gate misses observed in artifacts/phase0-mutation/enforced/20260423T053640Z for crates/tanren-bdd-phase0/src/main.rs (submit_lifecycle_transition mutants: delete ! and += to -=), by tightening behavior scenarios and/or implementation semantics so the final enforced mutation gate no longer reports unresolved misses and just ci can pass.","acceptance_criteria":[{"id":"t14-ac1","description":"Mutation misses in submit_lifecycle_transition are resolved.","measurable":"Mutation evidence no longer reports MISSED for crates/tanren-bdd-phase0/src/main.rs mutants at prior failing sites (delete ! and += -> -=), or includes explicit equivalent-justification triage linked to BEH-* IDs."},{"id":"t14-ac2","description":"Strict mutation gate passes in the enforced path.","measurable":"just ci passes check-phase0-mutation-gate with no unresolved missed/timeout mutants."},{"id":"t14-ac3","description":"Terminal repository health gate is restored.","measurable":"just ci exits 0 after remediation changes."}],"origin":{"kind":"investigation","source_phase":"do-task","source_task":"019db58b-b492-7423-925a-80190e82b708","loop_index":1},"status":{"state":"pending"},"parent_task_id":null,"created_at":"2026-04-23T13:28:03.545720Z","updated_at":"2026-04-23T13:28:03.545720Z"},"origin":{"kind":"investigation","source_phase":"do-task","source_task":"019db58b-b492-7423-925a-80190e82b708","loop_index":1}}}
tanren/specs/rust-testing-hard-cutover-phase0/phase-events.jsonl:376:{"schema_version":"1.0.0","event_id":"019dba86-f216-70f0-ba3f-6e657504827b","spec_id":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000c01","phase":"investigate","agent_session_id":"cli-session","timestamp":"2026-04-23T13:28:19.222915Z","origin_kind":"tool_primary","tool":"add_finding","payload":{"event_type":"finding_added","finding":{"id":"019dba86-f216-70f0-ba3f-6e51bc035260","spec_id":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000c01","severity":"note","title":"T13 blocked by weak mutation scenario plus acceptance-criteria ambiguity","description":"Failure evidence from just ci and artifacts/phase0-mutation/enforced/20260423T053640Z shows two MISSED mutants in crates/tanren-bdd-phase0/src/main.rs (submit_lifecycle_transition: delete !; += to -=). Root-cause classes: weak scenario (mutation survivor) and acceptance criteria ambiguity (reporting scope mixed with remediation scope). Investigation response split scope by revising T13 to require evidence-based terminal gate reporting/handoff and creating a dedicated remediation task for mutation-gate recovery.","affected_files":["docs/rewrite/PHASE0_ORCHESTRATION_META_READINESS_REPORT.md","crates/tanren-bdd-phase0/src/main.rs","artifacts/phase0-mutation/enforced/20260423T053640Z/triage.json","artifacts/phase0-mutation/enforced/20260423T053640Z/cargo-mutants.stdout.log"],"source":{"kind":"investigation","loop_index":1},"attached_task":"019db58b-b492-7423-925a-80190e82b708","created_at":"2026-04-23T13:28:19.222904Z"}}}
